definitions.definition: A form of entertainment popular in clubs , at parties , etc, in which individual members of the public sing along to pre-recorded instrumental versions of popular songs , the lyrics of which are displayed for the singer on a screen in time with the music .
An exercise in which the feet are alternately placed in front of each other while walking sideways to stretch various parts of the lower body and core .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) A form of entertainment popular in clubs , at parties , etc, in which individual members of the public sing along to pre-recorded instrumental versions of popular songs , the lyrics of which are displayed for the singer on a screen in time with the music .
